  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/b6bcae7ec30f5e5ef5e182042a2a4b83.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Welcome to the enchanting world of polyrhythms! <br>We thought nobody could beat this rhythm game, but the rhythm game gods proved us wrong and crushed it! So we’ve cranked up the volume and quality, and it’s back with a vengeance! <br>Can you conquer this rhythm? Bring it on! <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It’s a simple game where all you have to do is press the corresponding key the moment a circle reaches a vertex of a shape!<br>Well... the number of shapes will gradually increase, though... <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Stage select offers even more complex modes like Rest Mode and Offbeat Mode for those looking for a challenge.<br>Compete with your friends and see who has the best rhythm in the rankings!<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/7c921ee310209d5742594b5864a7f8ce.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/7c921ee310209d5742594b5864a7f8ce.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/7c921ee310209d5742594b5864a7f8ce.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Aim to become the next legendary composer </strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/b6bcae7ec30f5e5ef5e182042a2a4b83.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Welcome to the enchanting world of polyrhythms! <br>We thought nobody could beat this rhythm game, but the rhythm game gods proved us wrong and crushed it! So we’ve cranked up the volume and quality, and it’s back with a vengeance! <br>Can you conquer this rhythm? Bring it on! <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/8d0d47ec93d65002fde274d5c04fc35f.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It’s a simple game where all you have to do is press the corresponding key the moment a circle reaches a vertex of a shape!<br>Well... the number of shapes will gradually increase, though... <br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/ecfeda108cdfbc8bf38cc8330baa0d0a.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Stage select offers even more complex modes like Rest Mode and Offbeat Mode for those looking for a challenge.<br>Compete with your friends and see who has the best rhythm in the rankings!<br><br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/7c921ee310209d5742594b5864a7f8ce.poster.avif?t=1749704798\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/7c921ee310209d5742594b5864a7f8ce.webm?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006240/extras/7c921ee310209d5742594b5864a7f8ce.mp4?t=1749704798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Aim to become the next legendary composer </strong>",
